Here, we will compare mature neutrophils using their highly variable features

Where are the mature neutrophils in our entire neutrophil subset?

neuts$mat.neutrophil = neuts$active.ident %in% c("TREM1+MME+mat_neut","TNFAIP3+CXCL8+mat_neut","RETN+LCN2+mat_neut")
DimPlot(neuts, label = T, group.by = "mat.neutrophil")

lets pull them out and recluster them.

neuts.mat.sub = subset(neuts, idents = c("TREM1+MME+mat_neut","TNFAIP3+CXCL8+mat_neut","RETN+LCN2+mat_neut"))

neuts.mat.sub = RunPCA(object = neuts.mat.sub, features = VariableFeatures(object=neuts.mat.sub), genes.print = 10)
